d Jackson, 2003</a>], a chapter C<em>linical aspects of viral hepatitis</em> within the <em>Oxford textbook of medicine </em>[<a class=\"bibliography-reference internal-reference\" href=\"/topics/hepatitis-a/references/\">Hodgson, 2010</a>], and the BMJ Best Practice guideline <em>Hepatitis A</em> [<a class=\"bibliography-reference internal-reference\" href=\"/topics/hepatitis-a/references/\">BMJ Best Practice, 2018</a>].</p><!-- end field 4a75a75a-fffc-4549-b024-9e94b5ca5e13 --><!-- end item 0effb893-6bb9-4468-b64a-565c32a34f3b -->","subChapters":[]}]}}},"staticQueryHashes":["3666801979"]}